@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Notice";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Notice</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CDN -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome CDN -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }

        .notice-container {
            margin-top:15%;
            margin-left: 24%;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid black;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center vh-100">

    <div class="notice-container p-4">
        <h2 class="text-center text-decoration-underline">Notice</h2>

        <p class="mt-5">
            To,<br>
            <strong>Name of Theatre</strong><br>
            <strong>Theatre ID</strong>
        </p>

        <p class="mt-5">
            As per GPMC Act, 1949, Section 127(P), all the theatre and video theatres
            within the city limit of Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation (AMC) are liable
            to pay theatre tax (₹75 per show for theatre, ₹25 per show for video theatre).
            AMC has facilitated all the registered theatre owners to pay theatre tax
            through an online mode in the theatre tax module.
        </p>

        <p>
            It has been found that your theatre tax is pending since ......(Month)..........(Year).
            As a responsible citizen and owner of the theatre/video theatre,
            it is your duty to pay theatre tax on time. Kindly pay the due theatre tax
            to avoid penalty actions of AMC.
        </p>

        <p>
            For any complaint/grievance, you can log in to the AMC website and register
            your grievance in the theatre tax module.
        </p>

        <div class="footer text-end mt-5 ms-5 fw-bold">
            Assessor and Tax Collector
        </div>
        <div class="me-3">
            <p class="me-5 footer text-end ms-5 fw-bold">Theatre Tax</p>
        </div>


    </div>
    <!-- Send Notice Button Aligned to End -->
    <div class="text-center ms-4 mt-4 mb-4">
        <button class="btn btn-danger">
            <i class="fa fa-paper-plane"></i> Send Notice
        </button>
    </div>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 JS (Optional) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
